    <item>
      <title>避险需求推动美元录得一年来最长涨势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/dollar-set-for-longest-run-of-gains-in-a-year-amid-haven-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于地缘政治紧张局势不断升级，刺激对避险货币的需求，美元将创下一年多以来最长的周线上涨周期。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/dollar-set-for-longest-run-of-gains-in-a-year-amid-haven-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 10:00:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行关注科技领域投资者对美国股票失去兴趣的迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/bofa-says-trade-favoring-us-stocks-looks-at-risk-of-unwinding</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行策略师表示，纳斯达克 100 指数相对于标准普尔 500 指数的走势正接近某个水平，这可能引发有利于美国股市的交易的平仓。]]></description>
