      <title>欧元区私营部门意外陷入萎缩</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/euro-zone-private-sector-unexpectedly-slips-into-contraction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧元区 11 月份商业活动意外萎缩，这是政治混乱和贸易分歧加剧造成损失的迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/euro-zone-private-sector-unexpectedly-slips-into-contraction</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧元跌至 2022 年以来最低水平，因欧洲央行降息预期激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/bonds-jump-as-market-doubles-bets-on-half-point-ecb-rate-cut</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员押注欧洲央行将不得不大幅降息以提振该地区的经济，欧元跌至两年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-22/bonds-jump-as-market-doubles-bets-on-half-point-ecb-rate-cut</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 22 Nov 2024 08:44:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
